commit.title: [flags] [profile] Allow enabling the profile flag
commit.message:
[flags] [profile] Allow enabling the profile flag

IIANM, as of today Coq has the `CProfile` infrastructure disabled by
default, untested, and not easily accessible.

This draft PR is a step towards see what should be done with such
infrastructure, the first step is to actually allow enabling it at
runtime, even if unfortunately the whole thing seems a bit broken.
